p: Current version is release 1.2- a complete game, aside from potential patches in the future.
Would you like to play with the Traditional or Dark Story?
Traditional Story is a story more in line with the official Pokemon games, albeit with more characters, more plot and so on.
The Dark Story is a darker storyline.\nCharacters will die on screen, people will fuse with Pokemon, and the antagonists are cults.
Pick whichever one is more your speed! This can be changed in the Options menu, so feel free to try one or the other and switch later on if it's too tame or edgy.
